      <byline class="print_byline">By ANTONIO BETANCOURT</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Betancourt, Antonio</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Gunmen in Mexico kill Jose Nemesio Lugo, new chief of unit of attorney general's office that gathers and analyzes intelligence on organized crime, including drug traffickers (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Gunmen killed José Nemesio Lugo, a veteran government intelligence officer and the new chief of the National Center for Analysis, Planning and Information to Combat Crime, a unit of the attorney general's office that gathers and analyzes intelligence on organized criminal organizations, including drug traffickers. He was appointed to the post just a month ago.</p>
        <p>ANTONIO BETANCOURT</p>
      </block>
